<div class="niandai_zuozhe"> [唐] <a href="/chaxun/zuozhe/1.html">李白</a></div>
<div class="item_content" id="zs_content"><div><span>李白乘舟</span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid #999;margin: 0 1px;" class="zhushi_word">将欲行</span><span>，忽闻岸上</span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid #999;margin: 0 1px;" class="zhushi_word">踏歌</span><span>声。</span></div><div><span></span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid #999;margin: 0 1px;" class="zhushi_word">桃花潭</span><span>水</span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid #999;margin: 0 1px;" class="zhushi_word">深千尺</span><span>，</span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid #999;margin: 0 1px;" class="zhushi_word">不及</span><span style="border-bottom: 1px solid #999;margin: 0 1px;" class="zhushi_word">汪伦</span><span>送我情。</span></div></div>
